{"tid":2478924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場警署CID四人疑集體「蛇王」 男警旺角召妓遇掃黃「斷正」","createTime":"2021-04-07T12:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T14:43:12.000Z","uid":227801,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ef789d9a6cf4d92c6b7904b62e783eaf01558c","tid":2478924,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210407/XNN46PZD6RF3LNE7KAH3BRGW4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210407%2FXNN46PZD6RF3LNE7KAH3BRGW4Q%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=27891d26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210407%2FXNN46PZD6RF3LNE7KAH3BRGW4Q%2F&h=ff70a6b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210407/XNN46PZD6RF3LNE7KAH3BRGW4Q/</a><br />\n警隊爆出集體蛇王事件。消息稱，機場警署一隊刑事調查隊（CID），疑開工時間「蛇王」，其中一人更前往召妓，不料撞正同僚掃黃查牌「斷正」，結果連帶爆出同隊夥計「蛇王」，驚動警隊高層。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，事發於去年8月，涉事男女警隸屬機場警署刑事調查隊，負責寫字樓文書工作。其中一名男警當日於旺角懷疑召妓，不料卻遇上警員掃黃查牌。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，發現該名男警身處旺角的時間，是機場警署剛下班時間，男警理應人在東涌，因而東窗事發，連帶爆出同隊另外2男1女同袍亦有份「蛇王」。據知，事發後4名警員已調職，同時接受紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n本報正就事件，今日中午已向警方查詢，但至晚上7時仍未獲回覆。"},{"pid":"102ee1d2647a3f967fec426eab10dad36bfaece5","tid":2478924,"uid":191300,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:06:25.000Z","msg":"臥底行動，代號《蛇王》"},{"pid":"e2f7613f4d84a165931af6f34f6f94e664ddefb5","tid":2478924,"uid":343050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"點解自己人都都要拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b91b0513f9f4f405a4557444be01b9ad7df2d1","tid":2478924,"uid":37055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"工作範圍嚟㗎傻閪報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1170f003dfab1c1cb801da36ac663035108566b4","tid":2478924,"uid":380132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit